<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><key>F</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Ngaihchiat le sifahnak ka in lioah khan, Ka thlarau Jesuh sinah zuan a
 duh ta, Kei sual retheimi na fa si ka duh ko, A zungzal Pathian keimah ka
 huppheng tuah

[C1]
   Nangmah chungah, ka huppheng tuah, Azungzal Pathian keimah ka
   huppheng tuah.

[V2]
 Chun hnangamnak le zan ngaihchiatnak lakah, Tukforhnak a tampi ka in
 lioah khan, Hi vawlei nun chung tilet tho lakah hin, A zungzal Pathian
 keimah ka huppheng tuah.

[C2]
   Nangmah chungah, ka huppheng tuah, Azungzal Pathian keimah ka
   huppheng tuah.

[V3]
 Ral he kan i doh caan a tampi tikah, A ka hupphengtu sin ka zoh i ka
 chimh, Hneksaknak rili chung tilet thawh tikah, Jesuh, ka thlarau
 hngatchannak nang na si.

[C3]
   Nangmah chungah, ka huppheng tuah, Azungzal Pathian keimah ka
   huppheng tuah.</lyrics>
<title>NA CHUNGAH KA THUP CH66</title>
<hymn_number>66</hymn_number>
</song>